About FortyTwo Inc.

FortyTwo is a funded, stealth mode, startup located in Mountain View, California. 

FortyTwo is a consumer web startup, targeting a fascinating solution which will dramatically help daily productivity problems of any web users. 

To achieve that, FortyTwo is hiring world class talent in the fields of Information Retrieval, Artificial Intelligence, Big Data Analysis and Social Graphs. As FortyTwo’s product is built to serve the mass web consumption, we are looking for engineers who are passionate about distributed system and quality in a DevOps and Continuous Deployment environments. 

FortyTwo’s main backend environment is based on the Scala programming language deployed on Play Framework using the Guice dependency injection. 

FortyTwo’s consumer facing side requires amazing front end engineers who specializes in javascript, css and browser compatibility. All frontend engineers must be passionate about user experience. 

To contact us, please send us your details at - jobs@42go.com

Specialties
Information Retrieval, Artificial Intelligence, Big Data Analysis, Social Graphs, Scala
Architect & Project Lead. Working on Eclipse Open Healthcare Framework (OHF), Healthcare Service Bus (HSB), and other stuff like Java (J2SE and J2EE)
